title: Huge 3BR 1 bath duplex near St. Paul Campus
posting_body: ['Como/Raymond 3BR/1Bath  Walk to Campus, close to Luther Seminary, Hamline College', 'Property Address', '2111 Gordon Ave | 1 | St. Paul, MN 55108', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'MBJ Development Corporation |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Elegant Victorian 1500 square foot 3 bedroom one bath unit located at 2111 Gordon Ave in North St. Anthony Park', 'It is right off the corner of Como/Raymond -- one block to Langford Park.', "It's a short a ten minute walk to Luther Seminary or attend classes with a five minute walk to the St. Paul Campus and free inter-campus bus.", ' Fireplace and French windows add to the old world charm.', ' This classic Victorian offers high ceilings, stained glass and picture windows, large dining room, and study areas.', 'Two of the bedrooms are larger than many living rooms.', 'It has a remodeled kitchen complete with lots of storage, dishwasher, and counter space.', 'The floors are lovely hardwood which adds to the splendor of this turn of the century Victorian.', 'There is off street parking  and plenty of on street parking, additional storage in the basement as well as coin op laundry.', 'Amenities', 'hardwood floors', 'stained glass window', 'French windows', 'dish washer', 'study nook', 'full basement', 'free off street parking', 'inter-campus bus', '5 minute walk to St. Paul Campus', 'Close to Luther Seminary', 'one block to Langford Park', 'on-line rent payment', 'on line maintenance requests', 'close to Hamline University', 'formal dining room', 'on site laundry', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,500', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,660.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,660.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
